=== 商業活動 ===
[[2011年法國網球公開賽女子單打比賽|2011年法網]]奪冠後，李娜的名氣和商業價值遞增。2012、2013和2014年度的福布斯世界百大運動員收入排行榜中，李娜榜上有名，分別排第81位、第85位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/profile/li-na/|title=Li Na|accessdate=2016-11-12|author=|date=|publisher=Forbes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132240/http://www.forbes.com/profile/li-na/|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>及第41位。李娜曾為[[三星電子|三星]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.afr.com/business/construction/li-proves-trump-card-for-sponsors-20120115-j3loz|title=Li proves trump card for sponsors|accessdate=2016-11-12|author=|date=2012-01-16|publisher=Fairfax Media Publications Pty Ltd|archive-date=2016-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112144011/http://www.afr.com/business/construction/li-proves-trump-card-for-sponsors-20120115-j3loz|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[賓士|賓士]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/43426736/Li_Na_Signs_Big_Endorsement_Deal_With_Mercedes_Benz|title=Li Na Signs Big Endorsement Deal With Mercedes Benz|accessdate=2016-11-12|author=|date=2011-06-16|publisher=CNBC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412121727/http://www.cnbc.com/id/43426736/Li_Na_Signs_Big_Endorsement_Deal_With_Mercedes_Benz|archivedate=2015-04-12}}</ref>、[[勞力士|勞力士]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rolex.com/zh-hant/magazine/sports-and-culture/tennis/li-na.html|title=网球-劳力士经典奢华的腕表|accessdate=2016-11-12|author=|date=|publisher=Rolex|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221220235/http://www.rolex.com/zh-hant/magazine/sports-and-culture/tennis/li-na.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[哈根達斯|哈根達斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sportseasia.com/portfolio/li-na-%E2%80%93-haagen-dazs/ |title=Li Na – Häagen-Dazs – SEA |publisher=Sportseasia.com |date=2011-11-07 |accessdate=2014-02-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221190153/http://www.sportseasia.com/portfolio/li-na-%E2%80%93-haagen-dazs/ |archivedate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>等多個品牌擔任大使及拍攝廣告。2014年7月，[[耐克|耐克]]的[[上海|上海]]新總部大樓以李娜的名字命名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://slide.sports.sina.com.cn/t/slide_2_794_68015.html?img=1289721#p=1 |title=李娜为“李娜”楼揭幕 |access-date=2014-07-29 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421101319/http://slide.sports.sina.com.cn/t/slide_2_794_68015.html?img=1289721#p=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

